title: Contact
---

You can get in touch with members of the Chicago LUG through our mailing list,
on IRC, or any of our social media outlets.


<h4>Mailing List</h4>
<div class="vevent">

Subscribe to the ChicagoLUG Mailing List, or <a href="http://groups.google.com
/group/chicagolinux-discuss">view the archives</a>. Our mailing list is hosted
by Google Groups.

<form action="http://groups.google.com/group/chicagolinux-discuss/boxsubscribe">
<p><label for="google_email">Email: </label><input id="google_email" type=
text name=email /><input type=submit name="sub" value="Subscribe" /></p>
</form>
</div>

