</div>

<h4>Inter-Relay Chat (IRC)</h4>
<div class="vevent">
<p>
We use the #chiglug channel on the OFTC IRC network for informal
conversations. Clicking on the link below will open a new tab, bringing you
into our IRC channel via the <em>Mibbit</em> IRC service.
</p>
<p>
Note that you may see names of other people in this channel, but they may just
be idling. In other words, don't be surprised if you don't get a response right
away. People will chat (or not chat) in this channel at any hour of the day or
night.
</p>
<p>
IRC Link
</p>
</div>
</div>
